<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قرأ ابن كثير <span class="c2">(هَاتَّيْنِ)</span> بتشديد النون <span class="c2">((٢)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
